Interface for a Program Tree Change set.  Objects that implements this interface track
 various change information on a program tree manager.

methods.javadoc: adds the program tree id to the list of trees that have changed.

methods.comment: adds the program tree id to the list of trees that have changed.

methods.javadoc: adds the program tree id to the list of trees that have been added.
methods.name: programTreeAdded
methods.comment: adds the program tree id to the list of trees that have been added.

methods.javadoc: returns the list of program tree IDs that have changed.
methods.name: getProgramTreeChanges
methods.comment: returns the list of program tree IDs that have changed.

methods.javadoc: returns the list of program tree IDs that have been added.
methods.name: getProgramTreeAdditions
methods.comment: returns the list of program tree IDs that have been added.
